        SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]

        WHERE [o].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionProductId]

    WHERE ([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 44) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 4) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC

INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [t0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]

    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]

    ORDER BY [o].[CreatedTime] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a2].[Username], [a2].[Password], [o3].[Description], [o3].[Id], [a2].[Id] AS [Id0], [o3].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o3]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a2] ON [o3].[AccountBuyId] = [a2].[Id]
    WHERE ([o3].[Active] = 1) AND ([a2].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[CreatedTime] DESC, [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c3]
    FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]
        FROM [Orders] AS [o]
        WHERE [o].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionProductId]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 1) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 2) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 44) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 4) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [t0].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [t0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a0] ON [t0].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[c] DESC, [t0].[c0] DESC, [t0].[c1] DESC, [t0].[c2] DESC, [t0].[c3] DESC

2024-01-12 17:00:10.834 +07:00 [INF] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command
Executed DbCommand (58ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]

        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], CASE

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c3]
    FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]

        WHERE [o].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionProductId]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Active], [a].[AuctionProductStatusId], [a].[ClosedTime], [a].[Code], [a].[CreatedTime], [a].[Description], [a].[FinalPrice], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[Search], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[Name], [p].[ProductBrandId], [p].[ProductCategoryId], [t].[Id] AS [Id1], [t].[AccountId], [t].[Active] AS [Active1], [t].[AuctionProductId], [t].[CreatedTime] AS [CreatedTime1], [t].[Description] AS [Description1], [t].[Feedback], [t].[FinalPrice] AS [FinalPrice0], [t].[Note], [t].[Note2], [t].[Note3], [t].[Note4], [t].[Note5], [t].[OrderStatusId], [t].[OrderTypeId], [t].[Price], [t].[Search] AS [Search1], [p0].[Id] AS [Id2], [p0].[Name] AS [Name0], CASE

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c], CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 1) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 2) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c1], CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 44) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c2], CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 4) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c3]
    FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]

        SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]

        WHERE [o].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionProductId]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)

    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [t0].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [t0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a0] ON [t0].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[c] DESC, [t0].[c0] DESC, [t0].[c1] DESC, [t0].[c2] DESC, [t0].[c3] DESC

        SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]
        FROM [Orders] AS [o]
        WHERE [o].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionProductId]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 1) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 2) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 44) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 4) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [t0].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [t0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a0] ON [t0].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[c] DESC, [t0].[c0] DESC, [t0].[c1] DESC, [t0].[c2] DESC, [t0].[c3] DESC

        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c1], CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 44) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c2], CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 4) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c3]
    FROM [AuctionProduct] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[AccountId], [o].[Active], [o].[AuctionProductId], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Description], [o].[Feedback], [o].[FinalPrice], [o].[Note], [o].[Note2], [o].[Note3], [o].[Note4], [o].[Note5], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o].[OrderTypeId], [o].[Price], [o].[Search]
        FROM [Orders] AS [o]
        WHERE [o].[Active] = 1
    ) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[AuctionProductId]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p0].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Active] = 1) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 1) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 2) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 44) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC, CASE
        WHEN ([p0].[Id] = 4) AND ([a].[RegisterClosedTime] >= @__today_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [t0].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p2] ON [t0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p2].[Id]
INNER JOIN [AuctionProductStatus] AS [a0] ON [t0].[AuctionProductStatusId] = [a0].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[c] DESC, [t0].[c0] DESC, [t0].[c1] DESC, [t0].[c2] DESC, [t0].[c3] DESC

    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE (((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id]

    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE (((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [o].[Id], [p].[Name], [a].[RegisterOpenTime], [a].[RegisterClosedTime], [a].[OpenTime], [a].[ClosedTime], [p1].[Name] AS [Name0], [p0].[Name] AS [Name1], [p2].[Name] AS [Name2], [o].[OrderStatusId], [o1].[Name] AS [Name3], [o].[Price], [o].[FinalPrice], [o1].[Color], [a0].[FullName], [o].[CreatedTime], [o].[Note], [a].[Id] AS [Id0], [o0].[Id] AS [Id1], [o1].[Id] AS [Id2], [a0].[Id] AS [Id3], [p].[Id] AS [Id4], [p0].[Id] AS [Id5], [p1].[Id] AS [Id6], [p2].[Id] AS [Id7]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    INNER JOIN [AuctionProduct] AS [a] ON [o].[AuctionProductId] = [a].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderType] AS [o0] ON [o].[OrderTypeId] = [o0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [OrderStatus] AS [o1] ON [o].[OrderStatusId] = [o1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Account] AS [a0] ON [o].[AccountId] = [a0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Product] AS [p] ON [a].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategory] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductCategoryId] = [p0].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [ProductBrand] AS [p1] ON [p].[ProductBrandId] = [p1].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Province] AS [p2] ON [p].[ProvinceId] = [p2].[Id]
    WHERE (((((((([o].[Active] = 1) AND ([a].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([a0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([o].[Id] = @__orderId_0)) AND ([p].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p0].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p1].[Active] = 1)) AND ([p2].[Active] = 1)
    ORDER BY [o].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a1].[Username], [a1].[Password], [o2].[Description], [o2].[Id], [a1].[Id] AS [Id0], [o2].[OrderId]
    FROM [OrderAccount] AS [o2]
    INNER JOIN [AccountBuy] AS [a1] ON [o2].[AccountBuyId] = [a1].[Id]
    WHERE ([o2].[Active] = 1) AND ([a1].[Active] = 1)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC, [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t].[Id2], [t].[Id3], [t].[Id4], [t].[Id5], [t].[Id6], [t].[Id7], [t0].[Id]
